# Test result output directory

- Save all test and measurement artifacts (T6 full logs, msbuild logs, counter extracts, long findstr outputs, UTF-8 copies of run logs) under:
  - `D:\HTS_ARM11_Firmware\HTS_LIM\HTS_TEST\test result`
- Relative from HTS_LIM repo root: `HTS_TEST/test result` (folder name contains a space; quote paths in shell).
- You may still write under `HTS_TEST/t6_sim/diag_results/` during a run, but always copy the deliverable outputs the user will open into `HTS_TEST/test result` before finishing the task.
- Apply in every future session for this workspace.
